course.subject: COMP
course.name: Final Year Thesis I (Honors Study Track)
course.description: Students must take the whole course series comprising COMP 4983H and COMP 4984H in sequence.  They are expected to conduct research work under the supervision of a faculty member, summarize their work in an individual thesis and make a presentation at the end of the sequence.  Enrollment in the course requires approval of the course instructor.  May be graded PP.
